snippet.textDisplay: I get that they want answers from her... But we all know the money that was meant for upgrading the system is obviously long gone, stolen and used on BMWs and Kentucky.... That's probably not her fault though, but what on earth has she been doing there for so many months ????  The SABC interview with her is amazing. Truly a genius.
